                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "L'abandon épaissit sa ronce parasite",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Dans tous ces gouffres morts, Styx, Achéron, Cocyte ;",
